## Use Cases

1. **Morning triage**: Run `/inbox` to see what needs attention
2. **Focus on urgent**: Run `/inbox --priority high` for critical items only
3. **Backlog review**: Run `/inbox --state backlog` to review deferred items
{{#IF_SLACK}}4. **Team sync**: Share open tickets in Slack for visibility{{/IF_SLACK}}

